<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7826> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7826" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Cos. 184. In MRR 1.374, on the Consuls, refer also to Liv. 39.33.1, and 52.4- 5. On Licinus in Liguria, refer to Liv. 39.45.3; 40.34.4.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/2371> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #2371" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Proconsul (Liv. 39.54.2). The Consul Marcellus ordered him to bring his legion to the new Gallic town in Venetia (Liv. 39.54.2). See D.- G., 5.98, no. 3." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/2336> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #2336" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Cic. Brut. 60; Liv. 39.32.5-13, and 44.11; Fast. Cap., Degrassi 48f., 122, 456f.; Chr. 354; Fast. Hyd.; Chr. Pasc.; Cassiod. The province for both was Liguria (Liv. 39.38.1 and 7). On Porcius, see D.- G. 5.98, no. 3." .
